name: Chaos and Order
description: Surrealistrasyon//Şerif Gümüşbaş//Mixed Technique//4000x4000 pixel//Everything could be mixed up. Fear prevents us from going into it, and the order of chaos cannot be discovered unless we are in it//Drawing is an impressive form of expression for me with its universal and differentiating structure for each viewer. And I like to use automatism as a tool to transfer the impressions I have gained while continuing to research and learn in many disciplines. Because I think this method is a symbolic, mysterious and striking way of expressing.
